modules.description: Provides methods to prevent the device from sleeping and to restore normal sleep behavior, working with boolean states and callback functions. Handles platform-specific interactions for Android and iOS through direct plugin integration. Used to keep the screen awake during critical user interactions or long-running processes.

Provides functions to prevent device sleep and re-enable it, using callback-based control. Operates with unit-returning functions for success and error handling. Used to keep a mobile application active during critical operations or user interactions.
